title: Avanti Home Security Safe RS88B Overview
description:
Avanti Home Security Safe - http://www.abt.com/product/59143/Avanti-RS88B.html

Features:
• Interior Capacity: .88 CF / 25 Liters
• Easily Bolted Down and Ideal Storage for Jewelry Most Laptops Cameras Passports Wallets and Other Items
• Guest Instruction Label
• Accessible by 3 - 6 Digit Code
• Operates Using Four (4) Standard AA Size Batteries
• Optional External DC Adapter Available for Easy Opening When Batteries are Low
• Manual Override Key Included
• Long Lasting Powder Coat Finish
• Easy to Use Electronic Control Panel
